6a29a84323eb84d669f5d793b","tid":2117040,"uid":127469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0f6e4d8e7e403840058cc4b2686b3890dfc04f5b","tid":2117040,"uid":226944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db1e8c68d55a2d5ed33280b452b76699e2d01bbe","tid":2117040,"uid":32204,"like":12,"dislike":23,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"bd07284449a4a8fb0142a12d61d98444c3406a4e","tid":2117040,"uid":40267,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"係咪第三期先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"係，入咗 Phrase 3"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:08:25.000Z","msg":"如果依個係講緊ChAdOx1 nCov-19依隻嘅話 篇報道就講緊早幾日個個消息 最近進入左phase 3 但依篇並唔係講緊phase 3好成功 因為好似話phase 3係過萬人做嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錯請指出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"Oxford呢隻係係Phase 3<br />\nPhase 3 係千人測試，另外仲有兩隻喺Phase 3 階段<br />\n一隻係中國製叫Sinovac<br />\n一隻係澳洲研發嘅，不過呢隻唔係專門針對Covid 19，而係加強相關免疫力<br />\n全部都係巴西同南非測試緊<br />\n<br />\nPhase 4就係greenlight，可以mass production for general use<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/ng-interactive/2020/jul/20/coronavirus-vaccine-tracker-how-close-are-we-to-a-vaccine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Fng-interactive%2F2020%2Fjul%2F20%2Fcoronavirus-vaccine-tracker-how-close-are-we-to-a-vaccine&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=415e68d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/ng-interactive/2020/jul/20/coronavirus-vaccine-tracker-how-close-are-we-to-a-vaccine</a><br />\n<br />\nIn phase 1 of clinical testing, the vaccine is given to a small group of people to determine whether it is safe and to learn more about the immune response it provokes.<br />\n<br />\nIn phase 2, the vaccine is given to hundreds of people so scientists can learn more about its safety and correct dosage.