src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"Oxford呢隻係係Phase 3<br />\nPhase 3 係千人測試，另外仲有兩隻喺Phase 3 階段<br />\n一隻係中國製叫Sinovac<br />\n一隻係澳洲研發嘅，不過呢隻唔係專門針對Covid 19，而係加強相關免疫力<br />\n全部都係巴西同南非測試緊<br />\n<br />\nPhase 4就係greenlight，可以mass production for general use<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/ng-interactive/2020/jul/20/coronavirus-vaccine-tracker-how-close-are-we-to-a-vaccine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Fng-interactive%2F2020%2Fjul%2F20%2Fcoronavirus-vaccine-tracker-how-close-are-we-to-a-vaccine&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhPwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=415e68d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/ng-interactive/2020/jul/20/coronavirus-vaccine-tracker-how-close-are-we-to-a-vaccine</a><br />\n<br />\nIn phase 1 of clinical testing, the vaccine is given to a small group of people to determine whether it is safe and to learn more about the immune response it provokes.<br />\n<br />\nIn phase 2, the vaccine is given to hundreds of people so scientists can learn more about its safety and correct dosage.<br />\n<br />\nIn phase 3, the vaccine is given to thousands of people to confirm its safety &ndash; including rare side effects &ndash; and effectiveness. These trials involve a control group which is given a placebo."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"學到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T18:26:19.000Z","msg":"Sorry 我應該補充返以免誤會，你本身個資料其實係無錯嘅 <br />\n即係個report係講緊Phase 1、2好成功，而家進入咗phase 3，而唔係講緊phase 3好成功<br />\n只不過Phase 3唔係萬人測試，而係千人測試<br />\n但又其實嚴格嚟講你唔係錯，因為個測試唔係1 take pass，而且會喺好多國家做，一次千人試，試多幾次就幾萬人甚至十幾萬人"},{"pid":"f38f936c263c8f92c66876cb02c3e03f30310e3e","tid":2117040,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dedf96ac8b14e557497a91fd4279e10c53f06f9","tid":2117040,"uid":147367,"like":0,"disli